    "description": "Grow your career with Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Guest Relations Manager for our Patna team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nZomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
